{"tid":801965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國勇者網友這3字罵習近平 慘被拘留又罰錢","createTime":"2018-09-01T05:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T07:13:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c1045561286534d0c7a0dc9af8ec76f40de1df08","tid":801965,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國相當在意人們用什麼詞來指稱領導人習近平，過往有網友為了習包子3個字被關22個月，維尼則是被中國網路查禁，近日有網友又觸犯文字獄，說了句「習豬頭」，被拘留又被罰錢。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報導，7月中，中國海南省三亞市有網友在微信群中說了句「習豬頭最近怎麼樣了，好幾年沒看新聞聯播了」，8月20日警方以「公然侮辱他人」為由，傳喚該網友到案調查，並處以行政拘留10天，罰款500元人民幣（台幣2200元）。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，有別的網友透露，身邊友人因為討論民主，或在修憲文章底下留言「你為什麼不去找長生不老藥，這樣你就可以永久當皇帝了」，被警察請去「喝茶」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2537881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2537881&d=SWLYNpYq6C6koax7h%2FOlHhxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=119b3067\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2537881&h=545b5cfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2537881</a>"},{"pid":"b05ae8dc431c8f490d305c2db4e3be2608e3fff5","tid":801965,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6483abef26f397cd3192fd3315062d9132c9657","tid":801965,"uid":22326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66ca0f05f86b0376e44ec766d47a20753b74c42","tid":801965,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:54:46.000Z","msg":"以後避諱唔用習字<br />\n用屎咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e3b3af395ef17d8db594145cef41bc846c5fac","tid":801965,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:56:35.000Z","msg":"台灣駡人好似係刑事<img src=\"/assets/faces